PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 2008-194 of January 31, 2008, which corrects the amount of hectares and acres stated in the order setting apart certain lands, including mines and minerals as an addition to KAWACATOOSE RESERVE No. 88, Saskatchewan. The correct amount of hectares and acres should be 257.985 hectares (637.49 acres) of surface lands and 258.595 (639 acres) of mines and minerals. (LT-08-31)
